data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_10","content":"16:<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable di\"/>\n22:<meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable di\"/>\n30:<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable di\"/>\n31:<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable dinners. Reserve your table today.\" />\n37:<style>@keyframes fonts-loading { 0%, 99% { color: transparent; } } html.wf-loading * { animation: fonts-loading 3s; }</style>\n38:<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n39:<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,400;0,500;0,700;1,100;1,400;1,700\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" defer=\"true\" nomodule=\"nomodule\" src=\"//assets.squarespace.com/@sqs/polyfiller/1.6/legacy.js\"