id: 44
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I found the source’s concrete brand cues: black/white identity, square outlined buttons, uppercase headings, narrow underlined form fields, logo image assets, moody full-bleed food/interior photography, and copy centered on fire, lamb, seafood, banquets, and private dining. I’m binding that into a dark, editorial restaurant system with a restrained ember accent and sharp borders."}

