id: 55
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Page rhythm: `index.html` will act as the polished concept hub with anchored multi-page sections for Home, Menus, Functions, Gallery, Contact, and Vouchers, plus local photo assets and preserved outbound booking/voucher/social links. The structure will alternate full-bleed hero, menu index, dining/functions split, beverage/gallery strip, and contact CTA so it feels like a restaurant site, not a SaaS landing page."}

